 Premières Nations et des Inuit constituent la matière première de ce livre. De nombreuses photographies les accompagnent. Elles témoignent d’une forme de sagesse, d’un regard nous parlant du passé et nous projetant vers l’avenir.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 0aIndians of North AmericaxMaterial culturezQuébec (Province). 0aIndians of North AmericazQu{acute}ebec (Province)xCivilization. 0aIndians of North AmericazQu{acute}ebec (Province)xHistory. 0aIndiansvInterviews. 0aIndiansxEthnic identity. 0aIndiansxSocial life and customsy21st century. 0aInuitzQu{acute}ebec (Province)xCivilization. 0aInuitzQu{acute}ebec (Province)xHistory. 0aInuitzQuébec (Province)vInterviews. 0aInuitzQuébec (Province)xSocial life and customsy21st century. 0aTraditional ecological knowledgezQuébec (Province). 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Anthropology / General.2bisacsh1 aKurtness, Jacques, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aTanguay, Jean, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2016z978311127380808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2016z978311127630440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978276372731840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782763727318423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782763727318/original  a978-3-11-127380-8  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2016b2016  a978-3-11-127630-4  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2016b2016  aGBV-deGruyter-alles